description:
In today's video, we are looking at the 1974 horror novel by Stephen King, Carrie, and the 1976 Brian De Palma adaption that cemented King as a mainstay in horror genre fiction. As well as some more attempts at sequels and reboots that came along the way.

Thank you so much for watching.
